title: Herby Beef Meatballs & Broccoli Risoni Salad with Dill & Parsley Mayonnaise & Lemon
description: Tonight’s dinner is lean, mean and extra green! We’ve got juicy beef meatballs sitting on top of a hearty risoni salad flavoured with your favourite green veg and a generous squeeze of lemon for extra tang. All you need is a drizzle of creamy dill & parsley mayo to pull this masterpiece together.
